1. **Include the `tocloft` package in your preamble:**

```latex
\documentclass{book}
\usepackage{tocloft}
```

2. **Generate the ToC using the `\tableofcontents` command:**

```latex
\begin{document}
\tableofcontents
```

3. **Section headings to be included in the ToC:**

Make sure you have section headings (like `\chapter`, `\section`, `\subsection`, etc.) in your document.

Here is a complete example:

```latex
\documentclass{book}
\usepackage{tocloft}

\begin{document}
\tableofcontents

\chapter{First Chapter}
Some text in the first chapter.

\chapter{Second Chapter}
Some text in the second chapter.

\section{First Section}
Some text in the first section.

